ions. For example, they're used to log you in, save your language preferences, provide a shopping cart experience, improve performance, route traffic between web servers, detect the size of your screen, determine page load times, improve user experience, and for audience measurement. These cookies are necessary for our websites to work."},{id:"c1",name:"Analytics",desc:"We allow third parties to use analytics cookies to understand how you use our websites so we can make them better and the third parties can develop and improve their products, which they may use on websites that are not owned or operated by Microsoft. For example, they're used to gather information about the pages you visit and how many clicks you need to accomplish a task. We use some analytics cookies for advertising."},{id:"c2",name:"Social Media",desc:"We and third parties use social media cookies to show you ads and content based on your social media profiles and activity on our websites. Theyâ€™re used to connect your activity on our websites to your social media profiles so the ads and content you see on our websites and on social media will better reflect your interests."},{id:"c3",name:"Advertising",desc:"We and third parties use advertising cookies to show you new ads by recording which ads you've already seen. They're also used to track which ads you click on or purchases you make after clicking on an ad for payment purposes, and to show you ads that are more relevant to you. For example, they're used to detect when you click on an ad and show you ads based on your social media interests and website browsing history."}]},{market:"fr-FR",bannerMessageHtml:"Nous utilisons des cookies facultatifs pour amÃ©liorer votre expÃ©rience sur nos sites Web, par exemple en vous permettant de vous connecter aux rÃ©seaux sociaux, et pour afficher de la publicitÃ© personnalisÃ©e en fonction de votre activitÃ©s en ligne. Si vous refusez les cookies facultatifs, seuls les cookies nÃ©cessaires pour vous fournir les services seront utilisÃ©s. Vous pouvez modifier votre sÃ©lection en cliquant sur Â«Â GÃ©rer les cookiesÂ Â» au bas de la page. <a target='_blank' href='https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=521839'>DÃ©claration de confidentialitÃ©</a> <a target='_blank' href='https://aka.ms/3rdpartycookies'>Cookies tiers</a> ",acceptAllLabel:"Accepter",rejectAllLabel:"Refuser",moreInfoLabel:"GÃ©rer les cookies",preferencesDialogCloseLabel:"Fermer",preferencesDialogTitle:"GÃ©rer les prÃ©fÃ©rences en matiÃ¨re de cookies",preferencesDialogDescHtml:"La plupart des sites Web Microsoft utilisent des cookies. Les cookies sont de petits fichiers texte placÃ©s sur votre appareil pour stocker des donnÃ©es destinÃ©es Ã  Ãªtre utilisÃ©es ultÃ©rieurement par les serveurs Web. Microsoft et nos partenaires tiers utilisent des cookies pour mÃ©moriser vos prÃ©fÃ©rences et vos paramÃ¨tres, vous aider Ã  vous connecter, afficher des publicitÃ©s personnalisÃ©es et analyser les performances de nos sites Web. Pour plus dâ€™informations, reportez-vous Ã  la section Cookies et autres technologies similaires de la <a target='_blank' href='https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=845480'>dÃ©claration de confidentialitÃ©</a>.",acceptLabel:"Accepter",rejectLabel:"Rejeter",saveLabel:"Enregistrer les modifications",resetLabel:"Tout rÃ©initialiser",categories:[{id:"c0",name:"NÃ©cessaires",desc:"Nous utilisons les cookies nÃ©cessaires pour exÃ©cuter les fonctions essentielles du site Web. Par exemple, ils sont utilisÃ©s pour vous connecter, enregistrer vos prÃ©fÃ©rences linguistiques, vous permettre dâ€™accÃ©der Ã  votre panier dâ€™achat, amÃ©liorer les performances, acheminer le trafic entre les serveurs Web, dÃ©tecter la taille de votre Ã©cran, dÃ©terminer les temps de chargement des pages, amÃ©liorer lâ€™expÃ©rience utilisateur et mesurer lâ€™audience. Ces cookies sont nÃ©cessaires au fonctionnement de nos sites Web."},{id:"c1",name:"Analytiques",desc:"Nous permettons aux tiers dâ€™utiliser les cookies