      <p class="alert-title" title="Introducing the AI-First Partner Transformation Playbook:  Navigating the Future of AI Business Solutions">Introducing the AI-First Partner Transformation Playbook:  Navigating the Future of AI Business Solutions</p>
      <p>February 11, 2026</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bottom-link" data-json="[{&quot;Description&quot;:&quot;&lt;p&gt;AI and agents are unlocking the next wave of organizational value—projections show potential value creation between $2.6 - 4.4 trillion (1), with 1.3 billion AI agents in market by 2028 (2). As AI and agents gain more traction in everyday work, customers are expecting these AI tools to fit seamlessly into their existing business processes—both mundane and mission critical.&lt;/p&gt; \n&lt;p&gt;Partners are taking a strong role in helping meet these expectations—striving to become Frontier Firms that lead the way for their customers.  While becoming “customer zero” showcases the incredible potential of agents to transform business, partners must also transform their services offerings and business models to address market compression and unlock unprecedented opportunities to accelerate growth and profitability.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;To help partners thrive in this dynamic environment, Microsoft has created the &lt;a href=\&quot;https://aka.ms/ABSTransformationPartnerPlaybook\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-First Partner Transformation Playbook&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, a strategic resource designed as a framework for action to navigate the fast-changing market.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;The AI-First Transformation Partner Framework: Build, Sell, Deliver&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;At the heart of the Playbook is the AI-First Transformation Partner Framework, which spans multiple, interconnected dimensions—build, sell, deliver, and organizational structure—to transform your practice and achieve AI-first growth. The playbook includes an &lt;a href=\&quot;https://aka.ms/ABSTransformationPartnerAssessment\&quot;&gt;assessment&lt;/a&gt; to determine your current state and define key areas of focus along with a strategic, actionable blueprint for driving your transformation.&lt;/p&gt;  \n&lt;strong&gt;Unlock 3x services revenue and dive into new value pools with agents&lt;/strong&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The “Build” section of the framework focuses on reimagining  service offerings and IP development to help you:&lt;/p&gt; \n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Shift services to AI-first, domain-specific offerings that transform client workflows end-to-end\n&lt;li&gt;Create a more diverse mix of services that optimize profitability and revenue and tap new vertical and functional value pools\n&lt;li&gt;Invest in unique IP that stands out—powered by proprietary agents and embedded or stand-alone industry-focused solutions \n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;strong&gt;Evolve your GTM and monetization strategies to succeed in an AI-first marketplace&lt;/strong&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The “Sell” section of the framework defines go-to-market strategies and business models that will help you:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Take an integrated GTM approach that provides outcome-led transformation roadmaps focused on industry and functional business needs\n&lt;li&gt;Pivot to an economic model that accommodates non-linear approaches to help de-risk, such as outcome-based commercial models or value-based pricing \n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;strong&gt;Bring together human + agents to transform service delivery&lt;/strong&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The “Deliver” section of the framework focuses on upskilling your talent and client-zero mindsets to scale AI transformation with consistent quality and efficiency. This section will help you:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;Develop a cross-disciplinary workforce with continuous learning mindset\n&lt;li&gt;Hire and train for new roles focused on design and delivery of unified, AI-led solutions\n&lt;li&gt;Establish a hybrid human + agents delivery model to optimize teams and accelerate customer success\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;Why This Playbook Matters&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The AI-First Partner Transformation Playbook is different from the typical practice guide—it’s a resource to help partners look one to three years ahead so that you can align priorities, benchmark readiness, and shape the roadmap for sustainable, AI-native growth. Paired with immediate practice development guidance, this Playbook empowers partners to build their blueprint for transformation in the era of AI and agents. Engage this Playbook as:&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A blueprint for action:&lt;/strong&gt; Translating the current market dynamics into a multi-year transformation roadmap across offerings, talent, IP, and operating model\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An internal alignment tool:&lt;/strong&gt; Bring cross practice leaders together to align on priorities, dependencies, and investments\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A capability development reference:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify gaps across the dimensions of the AI-First Partner Transformation framework and use the assessment to benchmark readiness\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;Get Started on Your AI-First Journey&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;ul&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Review&lt;/strong&gt; market trends &amp; partner impacts—Download the &lt;a href=\&quot;https://aka.ms/ABSTransformationPartnerPlaybook\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI First Transformation Partner Playbook&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to learn about navigating foundational shifts partners must make across Build, Sell, Deliver, and organizational structure.\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assess&lt;/strong&gt; current state and align priorities and investments—Use the &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=\&quot;https://aka.ms/ABSTransformationPartnerAssessment\&quot;&gt;assessment tool&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (approx. 30 min) to identify gaps across the seven dimensions and  benchmark readiness. Bring cross practice leaders together to align on priorities, dependencies, and investments.\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Develop&lt;/strong&gt; strategic plan and take action—Create a blueprint for action with strategic guidance to shape your 3-year transformation roadmap to AI-native, outcome driven, multi-agent delivery models. \n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;1.\tMcKinsey, Seizing the Agentic AI opportunity report, 2025&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;2.\tIDC Info Snapshot, Sponsored by Microsoft, 1.3 Billion AI Agents by 2028, Doc. #US53361825, May 2025&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&quot;,&quot;FileLink&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;FileLinkVideo&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;FileModifiedDate&quot;:&quot;2026-02-10&quot;,&quot;FileName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;Icon&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;ImportFilePath&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;IsActive&quot;:&quot;No&quot;,&quot;IsProtected&quot;:&quot;No&quot;,&quot;Link&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;LinkTitle&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;Owner&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;Paragraph&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;RowID&quot;:&quot;e0e9a8f7-6f3f-4a6c-95cb-f26199ba57dc&quot;,&quot;VideoThumbnail&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Description&quot;}]"></div>
  </div>
  
